          <div class="ingredient-desc">
            Powders may include natural flavors, sweeteners, or texture-supporting ingredients.
            Review the label if you have dietary preferences or sensitivities.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="science-strip">
        <strong>Important note about research:</strong>
        Research on individual nutrients or plant compounds does not automatically establish
        that a finished supplement product will produce the same effects. Review product-specific
        information carefully and consult a healthcare professional for personal advice.
      </div>

